  "text": "In order to evaluate different aspects of the proposed loadsharing architecture, we have conducted experiments on two different application benchmarks, namely PCS (Personal Communication System) and Traffic. For space constraint we cannot provide a detailed description of these benchmarks, which can anyhow be found in [CITATION_1] .",
